{
  "texts": [
    "The dataset was publicly accessible, allowing easy access for this research.",
    "The dataset details, including the number of samples and types of features, are discussed in [28].",
    "The dataset contained 162 whole-mount slide images with IDC tissue regions in whole slide images (WSI) of breast cancer gathered from the Pennsylvania University Hospital and the New Jersey Cancer Institute.",
    "277,524 images with a size of 50 x 50 pixel RGB.",
    "The dataset included in this study consisted of 162 breast histopathology samples that were stained with H&E."
  ]
}